| 批次检查点 | 至少包含 `lastCursor`、`processedCount`、`filePartNo`、`attemptNo`、`retryCount` | `contracts/scheduler/`、`contracts/query/`、`tests/worker/`、`tests/query/` | 接管继续、批次重试和压测证据 |
