docs\context\architecture-brief.md:243:- `src/workers/scheduler-worker.ts`: scheduler worker entry
docs\context\architecture-brief.md:244:- `src/jobs/cleanup-job.ts`: cleanup job entry
docs\context\architecture-brief.md:245:- `src/config/`: 配置加载入口
